These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
4 different pets are kept: lizard, dog, frog, cat
City: colone, new-york, nizza, boston
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, grey, blue, purple
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, december, june, july
 1. the person who likes grey is not to the right of the person who likes chestnut##8
 2. the person who's birthday is in february is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##8
 3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who likes chestnut is not to the left of the person who likes purple##8
 5. the person who's birthday is in february is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##8
 6. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
 7. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the right of the owner of the lizard##5
 8. the person traveling to boston is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who likes grey##2
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is the person traveling to nizza##1
10. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
11. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3
12. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the dog##5
13. the person traveling to nizza is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##8
14. the owner of the dog is the person who's birthday is in june##1
15. the owner of the dog is not the person who likes grey##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Pet         | lizard     | dog   | cat | frog |
| City   | new-york | boston   | colone   | nizza  |
| Color         | grey  | blue  | purple  | chestnut |
| Birthday     | february    | june | december     | july    |

