.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  social-worker, nurse, architect, analyst
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, trike, van, motorbike
There are 4 different favourite colors: ebony, aquamarine, red, ivory
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, pakistani, egyptian, dutch
 1. the person who likes red is between the brazilian and the person who likes aquamarine##2
 2. the nurse is not to the right of the pakistani##8
 3. the nurse is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
 4. the social-worker is not to the right of the dutch##8
 5. the brazilian is not to the left of the person who likes aquamarine##8
 6. the person driving the motorbike is not to the right of the analyst##8
 7. the egyptian is somewhere to the left of the dutch##5
 8. the egyptian is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who likes ebony is the pakistani##1
10. the person who likes red is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
11. the brazilian is not to the left of the person who likes red##8
12. the analyst is on the left of the nurse##1
13. the person who likes ivory is somewhere to the right of the person driving the trike##5
14. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left or right of the person who likes red##3
15. the social-worker is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
17. the social-worker is not to the right of the person who likes aquamarine##8
18. the person driving the trike is not to the right of the pakistani##8
19. the analyst is on the right of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
