10. the gothic-revival house is the person who's birthday is in february##1
11. the person who's birthday is in september is not to the right of the person driving the skateboard##8
12. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
13. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
14. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
