 4. the fan of rock is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
 5. the person who likes mauve is not to the right of the dannemann-smoker##8
 6. the fan of country is not to the right of the person who likes mauve##8
 7. the fan of electronic is not to the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##8
 8. the bolivar-smoker is the person who likes azure##1
 9. the ritmeester-smoker is not to the left of the person traveling to paris##8
10. the person who likes orange is not to the left of the person who likes mauve##8
11. the fan of gospel is between the person traveling to paris and the person who likes azure##2
12. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the fan of country##1
13. the bolivar-smoker is not to the right of the person who likes azure##8
14. the fan of electronic is on the left or right of the person who likes azure##3

.:: Answer ::.
