.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-6::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, cranberry, pear, onion
House: gothic-revival, cottage, futuristic, art-deco
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, hip-hop, disco, country
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, adventure, family, time-travel
 1. the person watching family movies is somewhere to the left of the person eating cabbage##5
 2. the person watching musical movies is not to the left of the art-deco house##8
 3. the person watching musical movies is not to the left of the person eating onion##8
 4. the person eating pear is somewhere to the right of the person eating onion##5
 5. the person watching family movies is the fan of disco##1
 6. the person eating cabbage is not to the right of the fan of hip-hop##8
 7. the person eating cranberry is not the fan of country##6
 8. the cottage house is somewhere between the person watching family movies and the person eating cranberry##7
 9. the person watching family movies is somewhere to the right of the cottage house##5
10. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the cottage house##3
11. the futuristic house is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
12. the cottage house is not the fan of funk##6
13. the fan of hip-hop is somewhere to the right of the person eating cranberry##5
14. the person eating pear is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
15. the person watching musical movies is not to the right of the cottage house##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| Food      | cranberry    | onion   | pear        | cabbage  |
