 3. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bus##5
 4. the person who's hobby is fishing is not the person driving the boat##6
 5. the person driving the taxi is not to the left of the person driving the train##8
 6. the fonseca-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to liverpool##5
 7. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
 8. the person traveling to new-york is not to the right of the fonseca-smoker##8
 9. the person driving the train is somewhere between the person traveling to liverpool and the person driving the bus##7
10. the person driving the train is not to the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##8
11. the person driving the train is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##5
12. the bongani-smoker is not to the right of the person driving the taxi##8
13. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
14. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
