 4. the person who likes red is the owner of the cat##1
 5. the owner of the ferret is in an even position##4
 6. the cape-cod house is somewhere between the owner of the goldfish and the owner of the frog##7
 7. the cape-cod house is not to the left of the farmhouse house##8
 8. the palace house is somewhere between the person who's sport is soccer and the person who's sport is parkour##7
 9. the person who likes coral is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person who likes black is not to the left of the person who likes black##8
11. the person who likes coral is on the far left##1
12. the person who likes green is on the far right##1
13. the cape-cod house is the person who's sport is soccer##1
14. the person who's sport is soccer is not to the left of the owner of the frog##8
15. the palace house is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5
16. the person who likes black is not to the left of the person who's sport is swimming##8

